8.000Z","msg":"啱呀 根本唔會fc"},{"pid":"4661d63a3f9dc603344fea00f500919f82719e31","tid":1472812,"uid":279689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"老實講，澳門同大陸冇分別<br />\n你睇立法會有幾個民主派就知<br />\n<br />\n得罪d講，市民只關心幾時派錢"},{"pid":"c802164df59dd15b849ee4da9952a451825351b7","tid":1472812,"uid":52558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"利申澳豬先<br />\n樓豬唔好灰，we7朋友圈質素係咁上下。<br />\n不過我會嘗試拉返起佢地，<br />\n有時都會覺得好孤獨。<br />\n點解身邊啲人可以咁痴線？<br />\n佢地真係可以話俾你知佢地係on9"},{"pid":"f41cb31b1022269bb551cc12bf4747f7c9142b28","tid":1472812,"uid":28202,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"53c11de0b6cecaf414bcc0a9413e063bf5377886","tid":1472812,"uid":4527,"like":100,"dislike":1,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"你地有23條，講野小心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:07.000Z","msg":"唔講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳門跟香港有一個不同，根據澳門的《基本法》第27條，澳門人發起集會、遊行，根本不需要像香港那樣，向警方申請「不反對通知書」，只要提前「通知」警方就可以了。並且，澳門法律規定，干擾合法集會、遊行，屬於刑事犯罪。"},{"pid":"188ce67996b98afdd32f2d30db592d38e71e8636","tid":1472812,"uid":12034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20151221/photo/1221-00176-013b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151221%2Fphoto%2F1221-00176-013b1.jpg&h=a9da1127&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bf7bdf314f04c89d7e97f6a83bc56d9e52a7761","tid":1472812,"uid":58911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"我只係覺得好可悲<br />\n<br />\n澳門同香港隔一個海<br />\n<br />\n點解會被溫水煮蛙溫到咁樣<br />\n<br />\n我前一排不停咁播關於反送中真相俾屋企睇<br />\n<br />\n佢地深藍到無得再藍...<br />\n<br />\n依家又見到成班平時對時事莫不關心又係到食人血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n一個「愛國主義」就可以睇出邊個係藍絲<br />\n<br />\n真係好心痛 好難受 ...<br />\n<br />\n有朋友叫我話 keep著去同身邊既講<br />\n<br />\n但事到如今仲有得點講<br />\n<br />\n我好想放棄依個我鐘意左好多年既澳門...<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944a615d745fe8686a7721f9d876e6ca55b4a3a1","tid":1472812,"uid":162533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cf9e6832bff2520f52619c2b0fc21308d395cba","tid":1472812,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:52:54.000Z","msg":"佢地係因為利益定純on9先？<br />\n做生意果d？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"你以為澳門咁多老細？<br />\n更多既人人云亦云<br />\n藍絲廢佬話「搞亂」「收錢」佢地又跟住講"},{"pid":"2299764a1c5a97578c14031425599eff9d9d3998","tid":1472812,"uid":264457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:24:00.000Z","msg":"澳門=大陸，其實真係冇得救，人口60幾萬應該大陸移民佔過半，重點搞？"},{"pid":"b10c0ba55293970d92711d8fd2e7d1337d829658","tid":1472812,"uid":259993,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d3e933a06078bdcf13d9ae1be5b31223634b0a1","tid":1472812,"uid":58911,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"我真係心痛到喊出黎 點解我身邊既人變到咁<br />\n<br />\n溫水煮蛙真係煮到咁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"好撚慘 聽過有台灣遊客話去澳門喺講去大陸 完全冇當澳門喺SAR"},{"pid":"1ddd95fe49a69160ddd8b467484d0a0d8b6e1201","tid":1472812,"uid":178714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7134c68000e195fb73298bbe345ad6c53af9c71b","tid":1472812,"uid":138820,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:05:59.000Z","msg":"多謝你支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早兩個禮拜去澳門睇演唱會，發現澳門赤化問題好嚴重<br />\n喺威尼斯人啲員工已經好習慣一開口就講普通話<br />\n有啲仲唔識廣東話（大陸人嚟香港都要學講啦屌）<br />\n反而去珠海啲人講廣東話仲自然同多過澳門人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:32:20.000Z","msg":"試過去食嘢問個侍應收唔收信用卡佢聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87a743845209116793cfa926cbc9a3814b19626","tid":1472812,"uid